{"tid":1653004,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［必入］仆街政府咁好死批集會？合法集會蒙唔蒙面？","createTime":"2019-10-14T01:56:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T04:44:46.000Z","uid":52772,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1116c7c7ead4893d064c66bf1256e452d4b80139","tid":1653004,"uid":52772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T01:56:19.000Z","msg":"蒙面=公安拉鳩你，亦都係實驗合法集會以蒙面法檢控<br />\n<br />\n唔蒙=政府話蒙面法有用，我地屈服左係蒙面法嘅威脅<br />\n<br />\n當然合法集會不嬲好多人都唔戴口罩<br />\n政府拋返個波比大家，充滿智慧嘅連登仔，<br />\n依個陷阱大家點拆？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae1a9817c9b0dfd1670fe5f4194416ae596e9499","tid":1653004,"uid":288351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T01:58:59.000Z","msg":"想蒙咪蒙。我諗唔蒙果d大部份係真和理非。我就蒙"},{"pid":"a99bdd9342794fd596faa908907864f715b8363b","tid":1653004,"uid":288351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ae1a9817c9b0dfd1670fe5f4194416ae596e9499","tid":1653004,"uid":288351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T01:58:59.000Z","msg":"想蒙咪蒙。我諗唔蒙果d大部份係真和理非。我就蒙"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T01:59:51.000Z","msg":"集咩會。我係蒙面行街咁岩見到多人湊熱鬧。"},{"pid":"1c2a2093b893248ace97644dfc1066e029956ab9","tid":1653004,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:06:07.000Z","msg":"唔蒙就玩秋後算帳"},{"pid":"0ef972a6960bc02a88fd3df29cb9b40544dc116a","tid":1653004,"uid":170812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:06:51.000Z","msg":"人多防流感"},{"pid":"5dd06beef7e58d44bdad930cb5738feccd5367f1","tid":1653004,"uid":52772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:07:05.000Z","msg":"補充返少少，<br />\n如果係平時行街發夢，大家自然有共識係蒙面black bloc<br />\n咁合法集會，如今晚人權法集會呢？<br />\n如果真和理非大家都唔蒙面<br />\n變相比左政府有口實，拿，連支持示威嘅人都唔蒙<br />\n證明蒙面法大家都認同，合理法條例"},{"pid":"b93ca50391caefca00f2e4c9191ea835aed4ab1c","tid":1653004,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:13:48.000Z","msg":"病都唔俾？"},{"p